<item>
            <title>[LU-17835] sanity-krb5 test_5: lsvcgssd does not restart automatically</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17835</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Aur&#233;lien Degr&#233;mont &amp;lt;adegremont@nvidia.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/642a04f5-99ee-44bb-a549-2398f93e1d2c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/642a04f5-99ee-44bb-a549-2398f93e1d2c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_5 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/usr/sbin/lsvcgssd should restart automatically
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/104646&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/104646&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-362.18.1.el9_3.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/104646&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/104646&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-362.18.1_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_5 and several tests after this one (8, 9, ...) failed as lsvcgssd is killed and for some reason did not restarted, even if it is supposed to do so automatically.&lt;/p&gt;







